__SqlaTable__.sql: select "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )")) As Gender, AVG(Total) As perf,  AVG(Total) As dummy_perf, Count('District') as number_ from classes GROUP BY "District", TRIM(LOWER("Sex ( Male / Female )"))

SELECT "District", CAST("class" AS STRING) AS "class", (CAST(Total_Score AS FLOAT) / CAST(max_score AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Performance
FROM (  SELECT "District", "class", sum(Total) as "Total_Score", count(*) * 20 as "max_score"
        FROM classes
        GROUP BY "District", "class" ) AS A

SELECT *, (CAST(Total_Score AS FLOAT) / CAST(max_score AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Performance
FROM (  SELECT "District", sum(Total) as "Total_Score", count(*) * 20 as "max_score"
        FROM classes
        GROUP BY "District" ) AS A

SELECT "District", CAST("class" AS STRING) AS "class", (CAST(Total_Score AS FLOAT) / CAST(max_score AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Performance,
       (CAST(Total_Q1 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q1_Performance,
       (CAST(Total_Q2 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q2_Performance,
       (CAST(Total_Q2 AS FLOAT) / CAST(child_count AS FLOAT)) * 100 AS Q3_Performance
FROM (  SELECT "District", "class", sum(Total) as "Total_Score", count(*) * 20 as "max_score", count(*) as "child_count",
               sum("Q1") as "Total_Q1",
               sum("Q2") as "Total_Q2",
               sum("Q3") as "Total_Q3"
        FROM classes
        GROUP BY "District", "class" ) AS A
